pull_request.title: Bump oqs-sys/liboqs from `5b8e2bd` to `bcc94da`
pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `5b8e2bd` to `bcc94da`.
Commits
  • bcc94da Suppress constant time check for public matrix generation on Kyber AVX2 (#1189)
  • See full diff in compare view

pull_request.title: Update to current official libssh master branch
pull_request.body:
This update introduces some deprecation warnings during build, because an API has since been deprecated but is still referenced in test code.

This PR **must** be merged as a regular merge commit, not a squash commit, so that upstream merges will continue to work properly.
